If you want a specific unit constructed, you can direct me to locate an idle facility and build that unit to a destination of your choosing.  To instruct me to build a unit, close this message window, right-click on my image in the Command Center, select 'Build Ships', 'Build Troops' or 'Build Facilities' from my pop-up menu, and use the target cursor to select a destination to which the unit should be built.  The Build Window will then come up, from which you should select the unit and quantity of that unit which you wish me to build.  Once you have made your selections, click on the check-mark at the bottom of the build window so that I may act upon your request.